description:
Today on the show we had Cesar Pina along with his wife call in where he spoke about turning his focus to real estate, mastering the market and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man accused of domestic violence and caught on Zoom hearing in the same house as alleged victim and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
